tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:56:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你可能真係要睇下有乜野可以改善下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nface</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能真係要執吓個look<br />\n唔係話要搞到Mk look<br />\n但執一執可以好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥面點執？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我都係肥面，出面大把人肥面大肚腩都有女有老婆啦"},{"pid":"421c51b74befd60c08dcb70ffe688cf3d51b665d","tid":45140,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T19:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係絲定巴先，兩邊唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有少少身體接觸，咧如掂下手仔。<br />\n引他請你看戲，咧如你問他你覺得近排邊套戲好看，之後你話我都有興趣，但唔好你開口先話一起去看，你要表現出對套戲好有興趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c066759fcd785104eb03823384dbeefb706bbd4","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:11:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有少少身體接觸，咧如掂下手仔。<br />\n引他請你看戲，咧如你問他你覺得近排邊套戲好看，之後你話我都有興趣，但唔好你開口先話一起去看，你要表現出對套戲好有興趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打入對方既生活<br />\n等佢習慣你既存在<br />\n令佢會主動分享快樂既事<br />\n攻其所好<br />\n平時傾計要輕鬆幽默<br />\n間中加一兩句曖昧既說話<br />\n不過適當既時候要成熟認真<br />\n呢種反差幾有效<br />\n<br />\n記住唔好單靠感動去追求<br />\n感動佢係大絕要係就得手既時候用<br />\n更加唔好未一齊就做對方既心情垃圾桶<br />\n要令對方一諗起你係諗係開心既事而唔係諗係佢同你講既各種煩惱<br />\n<br />\n同埋最後<br />\n唔好太多內心小劇場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72085a33bcd956f551407235cbb0cc76795b560","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T21:17:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能真係要執吓個look<br />\n唔係話要搞到Mk look<br />\n但執一執可以好唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥面點執？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我都係肥面，出面大把人肥面大肚腩都有女有老婆啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥面真係唔係問題<br />\n一街肥仔都有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ff0972f74cbd5efb9154e27de144e979496d3b","tid":45140,"uid":48934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"35歲<br />\n未拍過拖<br />\n未破處<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"d7e1042ef6448e15144577ba8fb488933291f475","tid":45140,"uid":18496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>35歲<br />\n未拍過拖<br />\n未破處<br />\n點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以後個樣"},{"pid":"d8375899da1958a05c7fe75a355e63bcc0cc4a9c","tid":45140,"uid":18496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥面點執？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我都係肥面，出面大把人肥面大肚腩都有女有老婆啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥面真係唔係問題<br />\n一街肥仔都有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔明我點解無"},{"pid":"8abf2cf6bff7ec4066a349a8fe420fc0622a0812","tid":45140,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:40:57.000Z","msg":"見到好多以後既自己<br />\n我應該18就去叫雞<br />\n而家20 隻腳有傷口 好番就去<br />\n希望係新年之前做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e54b622ac6062b8e7523f951ac00731601dee8","tid":45140,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:44:27.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n23歲半鳥"},{"pid":"da67ccbcbdee9bde447b06b8f4157290607e1323","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:45:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我都係肥面，出面大把人肥面大肚腩都有女有老婆啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肥面真係唔係問題<br />\n一街肥仔都有拖拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我都唔明我點解無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原因黎唔開得幾個<br />\n自身性格問題<br />\n技巧不足<br />\n無岩既對象<br />\n<br />\n同埋女仔係要用吸引而唔係單純既追求"},{"pid":"a3c030036ed5d08321809504860693bdd4ccd51f","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:46:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到好多以後既自己<br />\n我應該18就去叫雞<br />\n而家20 隻腳有傷口 好番就去<br />\n希望係新年之前做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實無乜意思<br />\n俾你叫完如果你滿足既話就只可以証明你需要既係一個洩慾對象<br />\n不過係大多數情況下叫完只會空虛<br />\n因為無愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1061b02adc433b4377f2e133fc089dbaaf2302f3","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>35歲<br />\n未拍過拖<br />\n未破處<br />\n點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自身問題係主因<br />\n唔排除係因為你無鐘意既對象"},{"pid":"6a81bbf20719ac02e2301779ba5c2ab0ffa7a92c","tid":45140,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬a0教人溝仔#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"5a688774b775abe061de735660e9ca023b2fb591","tid":45140,"uid":60291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />fatc"},{"pid":"6f21cfef126ac2dfc02a8b9cfb685cf3d82a3338","tid":45140,"uid":59287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>35歲<br />\n未拍過拖<br />\n未破處<br />\n點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自身問題係主因<br />\n唔排除係因為你無鐘意既對象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你自己點睇35 仲係a0"},{"pid":"c83078e4901bdf6f8983f8d9d5521d3ea95b09ea","tid":45140,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:53:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬a0教人溝仔#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc #<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真返先<br />\n其實有時緣份既野好難講<br />\n裝備好自己<br />\n佢請你食檸檬咪下個<br />\n你先23大把世界"},{"pid":"b08feba85299092b14ae8660dc9cd04ace98b577","tid":45140,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有少少身體接觸，咧如掂下手仔。<br />\n引他請你看戲，咧如你問他你覺得近排邊套戲好看，之後你話我都有興趣，但唔好你開口先話一起去看，你要表現出對套戲好有興趣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打入對方既生活<br />\n等佢習慣你既存在<br />\n令佢會主動分享快樂既事<br />\n攻其所好<br />\n平時傾計要輕鬆幽默<br />\n間中加一兩句曖昧既說話<br />\n不過適當既時候要成熟認真<br />\n呢種反差幾有效<br />\n<br />\n記住唔好單靠感動去追求<br />\n感動佢係大絕要係就得手既時候用<br />\n更加唔好未一齊就做對方既心情垃圾桶<br />\n要令對方一諗起你係諗係開心既事而唔係諗係佢同你講既各種煩惱<br />\n<br />\n同埋最後<br />\n唔好太多內心小劇場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好太多内心小劇場係咪啫係唔好ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900f9eae16e59f4df152838b3216317d710b22d8","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>35歲<br />\n未拍過拖<br />\n未破處<br />\n點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自身問題係主因<br />\n唔排除係因為你無鐘意既對象</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你自己點睇35 仲係a0</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一聽會覺得呢個人一係就唔想拍拖<br />\n一係就係社交/性格有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9959fa0f3b78b9a2deb63f04055686b755807a","tid":45140,"uid":28236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想知巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打入對方既生活<br />\n等佢習慣你既存在<br />\n令佢會主動分享快樂既事<br />\n攻其所好<br />\n平時傾計要輕鬆幽默<br />\n間中加一兩句曖昧既說話<br />\n不過適當既時候要成熟認真<br />\n呢種反差幾有效<br />\n<br />\n記住唔好單靠感動去追求<br />\n感動佢係大絕要係就得手既時候用<br />\n更加唔好未一齊就做對方既心情垃圾桶<br />\n要令對方一諗起你係諗係開心既事而唔係諗係佢同你講既各種煩惱<br />\n<br />\n同埋最後<br />\n唔好太多內心小劇場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好太多内心小劇場係咪啫係唔好ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好因爲對方既一個小動作同一句說話就將成件事無限放大<br />\n平常心去面對"},{"pid":"e6ca6f5837279a98e599dcb3aa0bf9009309043d","tid":45140,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T05:00:54.000Z","msg":"正常"},{"pid":"1c54493320db185b0898ef99348d0b86cb499b8a